joelib2.data
Class BasicElementHolder

java.lang.Object
  joelib2.data.IdentifierSoftDefaultSystem
      joelib2.data.AbstractDataHolder
          joelib2.data.BasicElementHolder
All Implemented Interfaces:
ElementHolder, IdentifierHardDependencies, IdentifierSoftDependencies
public class BasicElementHolder
extends AbstractDataHolder
implements IdentifierHardDependencies, ElementHolder

Element table. The definition file can be defined in the joelib2.data.JOEElementTable.resourceFile property in the BasicPropertyHolder. The BasicResourceLoader loads the joelib2.properties file for default.

Default:
joelib2.data.JOEElementTable.resourceFile=joelib2/data/plain/element.txt

See Also:
BasicPropertyHolder, BasicResourceLoader
